{"tid":2233759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛行服務隊前身: 皇家香港輔助空軍","createTime":"2020-10-07T11:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T13:15:32.000Z","uid":62063,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"296b2741544824ace2984b09657d4693c65b218c","tid":2233759,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"好多人對GFS嘅印象就係救火救人<br />\n但其實係保安局轄下嘅紀律部隊<br />\n協助執法都係佢哋嘅職責<br />\n<blockquote><strong>內部保安</strong><br />\n香港警察經常徵用飛行服務隊的直升機從事各項工作，包括空運人員、在上空進行交通監察，以及通訊等。此外，<span class=\"red\">飛行服務隊亦經常連同一名水警督察在空中巡邏</span>，搜索非法入境者和走私者。<br />\n由於<span class=\"red\">挑戰者605型定翼機</span>配備先進的儀器和可作長途飛行，因此<span class=\"red\">警方會經常徵用定翼機執行秘密的巡邏職務</span>，以偵緝走私、非法入境和販毒活動。</blockquote><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://www.gfs.gov.hk/tch/servicec.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gfs.gov.hk%2Ftch%2Fservicec.htm&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmcfSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=1322abd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gfs.gov.hk/tch/servicec.htm</a></span><br />\n<br />\n主權移交後GFS仍然用緊<span class=\"red\">美國軍用</span>嘅黑鷹直升機 (UH-60)<br />\n解放軍當年只有民用版嘅黑鷹直升機 (S-70)<br />\n特區政府後來稱黑鷹唔適合做搜救行動宣布退役<br />\n但有傳係購入零件有困難 (待FC)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZbhafj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZbhafj.jpg&h=732e2daa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到依家最新嘅H175 (EC175/直15)<br />\n係歐資Airbus同<span class=\"red\">中資</span>哈爾濱飛機工業共同研發嘅直升機<br />\n香港人上年應該見過好多次 <br />\n(btw灑螢光粉係毫無根據唔好以訛傳訛)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWdvvom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWdvvom.jpg&h=412b99de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gyfGp8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gyfGp8.jpg&h=b7e9981d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當年皇家香港輔助空軍機師-蔡照明 (綠衫)<br />\n英國國防部皇家空軍參謀學院,<br />\n英國皇家空軍中央飛行學院 畢業<br />\n去咗做<span class=\"red\">中國交通運輸部海事救撈飛行服務顧問</span> <br />\n中國交通運輸部救助飛行隊係佢有份建立同訓練(見圖)<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BadgesStory/photos/a.184922284886956/998928066819703/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBadgesStory%2Fphotos%2Fa.184922284886956%2F998928066819703%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmcfSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=cab00840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BadgesStory/photos/a.184922284886956/998928066819703/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n政府飛行服務隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxWhamh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxWhamh.jpg&h=c0fcb7d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國交通運輸部救助飛行隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhFReNR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhFReNR.jpg&h=ec2b7535&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4Lecy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4Lecy5.jpg&h=393bb125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機隊制服同香港非常相似"},{"pid":"4d66f810a569642c6a0693c0193654b086ee8b8b","tid":2233759,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"853c763217ca4bf5df71692f4230589712f92970","tid":2233759,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d66f810a569642c6a0693c0193654b086ee8b8b","tid":2233759,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23717d6259bbd9515867b2b7d25e9e91e313b564","tid":2233759,"uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7799601d93cabf0238bae73628e3021f5a9cc81b","tid":2233759,"uid":137704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"啲super puma原本係全部橙白色，除咗一部之外全部變咗灰黑色係因為配合popo做空降遊繩行動。"},{"pid":"586c065a16fd2eb91baeb4f627c97186258af2a5","tid":2233759,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7799601d93cabf0238bae73628e3021f5a9cc81b","tid":2233759,"uid":137704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"啲super puma原本係全部橙白色，除咗一部之外全部變咗灰黑色係因為配合popo做空降遊繩行動。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"睇維基，美洲豹已經退疫"},{"pid":"c3670fc218490ab4a6f8983d04793c9d609c5b2c","tid":2233759,"uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:35:22.000Z","msg":"皇家警察都變曱甴<br />\nGFS變飛曱甴好出奇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13cf3f43340e093f79cb3c965ee90a75784dfef","tid":2233759,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"飛曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4e88326d9fba37c47720ac821f16150c99fb5f","tid":2233759,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528189-20200525.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528189-20200525.htm&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmcfSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=926319b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528189-20200525.htm&h=44e83651\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528189-20200525.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">飛行服務隊表態支持「港區國安法」決定 稱已作好準備</span></span></strong><br />\n2020-05-25 HKT 13:36<br />\n<br />\n多個紀律部隊首長陸續表態，支持全國人大將審議建立健全香港特別行政區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制的決定。<br />\n<br />\n政府飛行服務隊總監胡偉雄表示支持決定，全力支持特區政府履行應有職責，竭力維護國家安全，政府飛行服務隊已作好準備，支持警方果斷執法，會全力支持特區政府推行草案，建立安全及穩定社會，確保香港長期繁榮穩定，長治久安。<br />\n<br />\n胡偉雄表示，過去一年香港出現的暴力不斷升級，巿民的生命財產受到越來越大的威脅及破壞，恐怖主義亦正在港滋生，危害國家安全的活動更越趨猖獗，令社會充斥暴力，失去安寧。"},{"pid":"59d3decb7650be5588fefc737aa23019ee53d01d","tid":2233759,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"586c065a16fd2eb91baeb4f627c97186258af2a5","tid":2233759,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7799601d93cabf0238bae73628e3021f5a9cc81b","tid":2233759,"uid":137704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"啲super puma原本係全部橙白色，除咗一部之外全部變咗灰黑色係因為配合popo做空降遊繩行動。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"睇維基，美洲豹已經退疫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"係，super puma同dolphins 都retired, 所以新買嗰啲全面配合驚隊全部都係灰黑色塗裝，原本出廠係泥黃色。"},{"pid":"bea1b8f5ffcd76ba460fe2290fa4e4cce5708e8a","tid":2233759,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:43:27.000Z","msg":"飛蟻"},{"pid":"221ef6199c8d66aff7b02acec7579ab4b4c2c100","tid":2233759,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e4e88326d9fba37c47720ac821f16150c99fb5f","tid":2233759,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528189-20200525.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528189-20200525.htm&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmcfSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=926319b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528189-20200525.htm&h=44e83651\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528189-20200525.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">飛行服務隊表態支持「港區國安法」決定 稱已作好準備</span></span></strong><br />\n2020-05-25 HKT 13:36<br />\n<br />\n多個紀律部隊首長陸續表態，支持全國人大將審議建立健全香港特別行政區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制的決定。<br />\n<br />\n政府飛行服務隊總監胡偉雄表示支持決定，全力支持特區政府履行應有職責，竭力維護國家安全，政府飛行服務隊已作好準備，支持警方果斷執法，會全力支持特區政府推行草案，建立安全及穩定社會，確保香港長期繁榮穩定，長治久安。<br />\n<br />\n胡偉雄表示，過去一年香港出現的暴力不斷升級，巿民的生命財產受到越來越大的威脅及破壞，恐怖主義亦正在港滋生，危害國家安全的活動更越趨猖獗，令社會充斥暴力，失去安寧。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd8451f3b34b88fad24c5eabe7fa3d11e1ca929","tid":2233759,"uid":269137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"支那一定順便用嚟偷飛行設備技術<br />\n當年部黑鷹隨時係俾人拆開研究玩壞咗"}]}